column5: Nice to see you guys back in your ,ZONE.
We fished out of Port D towards Jordan today, boated probably 20, lost more then I'd like to count.   Crazy day out there.
And you're still at it... Those 6 months just faded away in a day.
nice we have been out twice.  always picking the wrong days.  hope to get out soon but need to scratch my gobbler itch too!
